                    spreadRadius: 1,
                    blurRadius: 5,
                  ),
                ],
              ),
              child: Column(
                crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
                children: [
                  Row(
                    children: [
                      Icon(Icons.access_time, color: AppColors.orange, size: 20),
                      SizedBox(width: 8),
                      Text(
                        'Delivery Time',
                        style: TextStyle(fontSize: 16, fontWeight: FontWeight.w600),
